comments: Towns (MIN) firms up in a legal picking position in the path of Johnson (PHX).
Johnson (PHX) briefly places a forearm to Teague's (MIN) front as he moves around the pick, but the contact is marginal. Teague's reaction is not consistent with the contact.
Johnson (PHX) and Towns (MIN) briefly engage and disengage off-ball in the post.
Kaminsky (PHX) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Wiggins' (MIN) path.
Kaminsky (PHX) maintains a legal guarding position during Wiggins (MIN) driving shot attempt.
During the pick, Wiggins (MIN) briefly engages and disengages with Kaminsky (PHX).
Bates-Diop (MIN) makes contact to Booker's (PHX) body during his driving shot attempt.
Towns (MIN) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Bridges' (PHX) path.
Kaminsky (PHX) makes contact to Teague's (MIN) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Bell (MIN) makes marginal contact with Oubre Jr. (PHX) as he releases to retrieve the rebound.
Bell (MIN) legally contests the shot attempt by Booker (PHX).v
Johnson (PHX) makes marginal contact with Teague (MIN) during the rebound, but does not affect his ability to retrieve the ball.
Wiggins (MIN) makes marginal contact with Booker (PHX) during the rebound, but does not affect his ability to rebound.
Wiggins (MIN) commits a take foul on Booker (PHX).
Towns (MIN) slightly extends his arm to Johnson's (PHX) front, but does not affect his ability to defend.
